    <h1 class="display-lg">DSCR Loan: 7 Smart Strategies for Real Estate Investors to Qualify</h1>
    <p class="lede lp-lede">Qualify on the property's cash flow — not your W-2. Jim Blackburn · <span class="mono">NMLS #1072866</span></p>
    <div class="lp-cta-row">
      <a href="/same-day-approval/" class="btn btn-blue btn-arrow">See My Options</a>
